tips: Tip: Tenor GIFs are processed as MP4s by default due to their superior quality.
Tip: Use $tenorgif to get the raw gif file straight from tenor.
Tip: Use $videotogif and $giftovideo to convert between videos and gifs.
Tip: Media with more than 250 frames will not be processed by caption commands. use $fps to change the framerate.
Tip: Type $help `command` for more info on a command.
